---
title: Moroccan Honey Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Currants & Lemon Yoghurt
description: We love the way honey caramelises in a pan, lending a crispy, sticky finish to chicken. We’ve used chicken thigh here because it packs a fantastic flavour, remains moist as it cooks and complements the bed of delicious roast veggie couscous that comes with it.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/moroccan-honey-chicken-487264ec.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/moroccan-honey-chicken-5eb37ecf82465b60675c2c61-71129bed.pdf
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/moroccan-honey-chicken-and-veggie-couscous-5eb37ecf82465b60675c2c61
